DIY Pool by @5.min.crafts 
.
⚠️These are purely my opinions only. If you don’t agree we can still be friends.
.
Pros: 
1) Relatively easy DIY
2) Accessible material
3) Fastest way to get a pool this summer 
.
Cons: 
1) Pallet is expensive. This might cost as much as a nice portable jacuzzi 
2) pallets might not be strong enough to hold the water and the hydrostatic pressure 
3) requires quite a bit of work 
.
Let me know what you think or if I missed anything. DIY or D-I-Why?
.
.
